{"id":163438,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/global-voices-泰国：仆街照风潮之后/","date":"2011-06-23T22:30:26Z","modified":"2011-06-23T22:30:26Z","title":"Global Voices | 泰国：仆街照风潮之后","content":"<p><p>“仆街”照片一开始在泰国也很风行，<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.bangkokpost.com/print/242899/\" href=\"http://www.bangkokpost.com/print/242899/\">名人</a>、<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://suthichaiyoon.blogspot.com/2011/06/red-shirts-go-planking-at-ratchaprasong.html\" href=\"http://suthichaiyoon.blogspot.com/2011/06/red-shirts-go-planking-at-ratchaprasong.html\">抗议民众</a>、<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.bangkokpost.com/breakingnews/242741/chuwit-pulls-off-a-plank\" href=\"http://www.bangkokpost.com/breakingnews/242741/chuwit-pulls-off-a-plank\">政治人物</a>纷纷公布自己的仆街照片；Faceebook<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.facebook.com/bkkplank?sk=wall\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/bkkplank?sk=wall\">页面</a>“曼谷仆街社群”也随之成立，让一般民众上传自己在各种奇异场所的仆街照片。</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=1763526369187&#038;set=o.213766261988283&#038;type=1&#038;ref=nf\"><img title=\"planking\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/planking-375x280.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"375\" height=\"280\" /></a></p>\n<p>照片来自Facebook页面Princess OftheMoon YathAkira</p>\n</div>\n<p>以下这张仆街照片的主角身穿袈裟，在網絡上引起热烈讨论，甚至有人悬赏奖金，要找出照片中的这个人。</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yfrog.com/gy9o0jzj\"><img title=\"monk\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/monk-375x281.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"375\" height=\"281\" /></a></p>\n<p>照片来自yfrog页面CrimeWatchCH</p>\n</div>\n<p>“<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.nationmultimedia.com/2011/06/21/national/Nude-planking-photos-online-an-offence-30158300.html\" href=\"http://www.nationmultimedia.com/2011/06/21/national/Nude-planking-photos-online-an-offence-30158300.html\">文化观察中心</a>”强调裸体仆街照片“失礼”，但Saksith Saiyasombut<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://asiancorrespondent.com/57921/thailands-cultural-heralds-to-crackdown-on-planking/\" href=\"http://asiancorrespondent.com/57921/thailands-cultural-heralds-to-crackdown-on-planking/\">反对</a>这种言论：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>又是种“失礼”行为，仆街照片当然是没什么正面功能，只是种无意义的趣味，搏君一笑罢了。</p>\n<p>这些人士自诩为“文化先驱”，没有静静看着热潮退去（当今網絡风潮来去都快），反而小题大作，下回各位若要成为良好典范，请不要一切诉诸直觉反应，只想着要保护所谓的“合礼行为”，一笑置之即可！</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>仆街照片热潮很快就由“跪坐照”（<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.cnngo.com/bangkok/play/thailand-embraces-planking-and-gives-it-twist-592652\" href=\"http://www.cnngo.com/bangkok/play/thailand-embraces-planking-and-gives-it-twist-592652\">Pub Peab</a>）取而代之，心态大同小异，只是增添了泰国文化色彩。</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=238796602801067&#038;set=o.111894685567117&#038;type=1&#038;ref=nf\"><img title=\"pub peab monk\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/pub-peab-monk-375x250.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"375\" height=\"250\" /></a></p>\n<p>相关Facebook<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.facebook.com/pubpeab\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/pubpeab\">页面</a>已有至少200,339人支持，也设有<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://twitter.com/#!/Pubpeab_Th\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#%21/Pubpeab_Th\">Twitter帐号</a>。</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/pub_twitter.png\"><img title=\"pub_twitter\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/pub_twitter-375x181.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"375\" height=\"181\" /></a></p>\n<p>就连官方也<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.nationmultimedia.com/2011/06/21/national/Planking-with-a-Thai-slant-30158356.html\" href=\"http://www.nationmultimedia.com/2011/06/21/national/Planking-with-a-Thai-slant-30158356.html\">支持</a>“跪坐照”，认为有助推广泰国文化。</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=235203683162902&#038;set=o.111894685567117&#038;type=1&#038;ref=nf\"><img title=\"pub peab\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/pub-peab-375x281.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"375\" height=\"281\" /></a></p>\n<p>来自Facebook页面NuAe Pichaya</p>\n</div>\n<div>校对：<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"使用者:Soup\" href=\"http://proj.daodin.net/mediawiki/index.php/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80%85:Soup\">Soup</a></div>\n<p><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/mong/\" title=\"文章导读 Mong Palatino\">Mong Palatino</a> · 译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/leonard/\" title=\"文章导读 Leonard\">Leonard</a> </span> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/06/21/thailand-pub-peab-and-planking-craze/\" title=\"阅读原文 [en]\">阅读原文 [en]</a> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2011/06/24/9407/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br />分享: <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E6%B3%B0%E5%9B%BD%EF%BC%9A%E4%BB%86%E8%A1%97%E7%85%A7%E9%A3%8E%E6%BD%AE%E4%B9%8B%E5%90%8E&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F06%2F24%2F9407%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F06%2F24%2F9407%2F&#038;desc=%E6%B3%B0%E5%9B%BD%EF%BC%9A%E4%BB%86%E8%A1%97%E7%85%A7%E9%A3%8E%E6%BD%AE%E4%B9%8B%E5%90%8E\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/%22%20onclick=%22javascript:var%20js=document.createElement%20(\" title=\"Shouker\"><span>Shouker</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F06%2F24%2F9407%2F\" title=\"facebook\"><span>facebook</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F06%2F24%2F9407%2F&#038;text=%E6%B3%B0%E5%9B%BD%EF%BC%9A%E4%BB%86%E8%A1%97%E7%85%A7%E9%A3%8E%E6%BD%AE%E4%B9%8B%E5%90%8E&#038;via=globalvoicesz